dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Adams County, WI 2024
dc_description_s: This data group represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2024 and includes the layers 'ADAMS_ROADS_2024' and 'ADAMS_ROW_2024'. [Adams County ROW polygons]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://adams-county-open-data-portal-adams-county-wi.hub.arcgis.com/
